OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FThe sentence for selling knives to
OL,7,Funder 18s will be increased to a
OL,8,Fmaximum of two years, ITV News' North
OL,9,Fof England Reporter Amy Welch reports
OL,11,FStricter rules for retailers selling
OL,12,Fknives online, along with tougher
OL,13,Fpenalties for those who break the
OL,14,Frules, have been announced by the home
OL,15,Fsecretary.
