OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FYvette Cooper announced unveiled a
OL,7,Fraft of anti-knife crime plans,
OL,8,Fincluding making retailers report bulk
OL,9,For suspicious sales to police, and
OL,10,Fincreasing the jail sentence for
OL,11,Fselling weapons to children or illegal
OL,12,Fblades such as zombie knives, to two
OL,13,Fyears.
OL,15,FThe laws will collectively be known as
OL,16,F'Ronan's Law', named after 16-year-old
OL,17,FRonan Kanda who was murdered in
OL,18,FWolverhampton in 2022.
