OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FRetailers will be required to report
OL,7,Fany bulk or suspicious-looking
OL,8,Fpurchases of knives on their platforms
OL,9,Fto police to prevent illegal resales
OL,10,Fhappening across social media accounts.
OL,12,FThe sentence for selling weapons to
OL,13,Funder 18s will also increase from six
OL,14,Fmonths to a maximum of two years
OL,15,Fprison time, which could apply to an
OL,16,Findividual who has processed the sale
OL,17,For a CEO of the company.
