OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FThe law will also cover legal and
OL,7,Fillegal knives meaning the possession
OL,8,Fof any offensive weapon with intent
OL,9,Ffor violence will come with a maximum
OL,10,Fprison sentence of four years.
OL,12,FThe government is also exploring
OL,13,Fwhether to introduce a registration
OL,14,Fsystem so only responsible retailers
OL,15,Fare allowed to sell knives.
OL,17,FIt comes after the government has
OL,18,Falready announced a strengthening of
OL,19,FID checks required to buy knives or
OL,20,Fhave them delivered.
