OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FThe home secretary thanked the Kanda
OL,7,Ffamily paying tribute to their work in
OL,8,Fhelping bring about knife crime reform.
OL,10,FCooper said: "We are honouring our
OL,11,Fcommitment to introduce Ronan's Law in
OL,12,Fmemory of Ronan Kanda who was
OL,13,Ftragically killed in 2022.
OL,15,F"I am so grateful to the Kanda family
OL,16,Ffor their endless perseverance in
OL,17,Fensuring governments take the right
OL,18,Factions to protect young people from
OL,19,Ffurther tragedy."
