OL,3,C'Ronan's Law' to introduce stricter
OL,4,Crules on knife retailers
OL,6,FThe measures include plans to create
OL,7,Fan offence of possessing a weapon with
OL,8,Fintent for violence. Currently a
OL,9,Fsimilar offence exists for someone
OL,10,Ffound in possession of a gun, but not
OL,11,Fa knife.
OL,13,FA new national police unit to tackle
OL,14,Fonline knife sales will also be
OL,15,Fpiloted.
OL,17,FThe proposals do not include measures,
OL,18,Fhighlighted by actor and anti-knife
OL,19,Fcrime campaigner Idris Elba, for a ban
OL,20,Fon pointed ends on kitchen knives.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
